WEBVTT

00:00:02.000 --> 00:00:04.200
[Audio description] From the creators of Tangled and Wreck-It Ralph.

00:00:04.200 --> 00:00:06.000
[Audio description] Disney.

00:00:06.000 --> 00:00:08.800
[Audio description] A carrot-nosed, coal-eyed snowman shuffles

00:00:08.800 --> 00:00:10.600
[Audio description] up to a purple flower peeping out of deep snow.

00:00:10.800 --> 00:00:11.800


00:00:12.300 --> 00:00:13.300
[Audio description] Hello. He takes a deep sniff.

00:00:13.300 --> 00:00:14.800
[Audio description] His nose lands on a frozen pond.

00:00:15.200 --> 00:00:16.800
[Audio description] A reindeer looks up

00:00:16.800 --> 00:00:18.900
[Audio description] and pants like a dog.

00:00:19.000 --> 00:00:21.200
[Audio description] Seeing the reindeer slip on the ice,

00:00:21.200 --> 00:00:23.800
[Audio description] the snowman smiles and moves toward him,

00:00:23.800 --> 00:00:27.600
[Audio description] though actually he's running on the spot.

00:00:28.000 --> 00:00:30.300
[Audio description] The reindeer falls on his chin.

00:00:30.300 --> 00:00:32.800
[Audio description] The snowman uses his arm as a crutch.

00:00:32.800 --> 00:00:36.000
[Audio description] The reindeer paddles his front legs head over heels.

00:00:36.000 --> 00:00:38.600
[Audio description] The snowman crawls along the ice.

00:00:38.600 --> 00:00:41.200
[Audio description] The reindeer does the breaststroke.

00:00:41.200 --> 00:00:45.000
[Audio description] The snowman rolls his body, but flips onto his back.

00:00:45.000 --> 00:00:47.200
[Audio description] The reindeer's tongue sticks to the ice.

00:00:47.200 --> 00:00:49.100
[Audio description] The snowman, his head, twig arm,

00:00:49.100 --> 00:00:51.000
[Audio description] and reindeer lips tug at the carrot.

00:00:51.000 --> 00:00:53.900
[Audio description] The carrot flies off and lands in soft snow.

00:00:53.900 --> 00:00:56.900
[Audio description] The reindeer goes after it with the snowman

00:00:56.900 --> 00:01:00.000
[Audio description] and his body parts hanging on his tail.

00:01:00.000 --> 00:01:03.400
[Audio description] The snowman puts himself back together again

00:01:03.400 --> 00:01:08.000
[Audio description] and glumly contemplates his noseless state.

00:01:08.000 --> 00:01:10.900
[Audio description] The reindeer jams the carrot back in place

00:01:10.900 --> 00:01:13.400
[Audio description] and pants like a proud puppy.

00:01:13.400 --> 00:01:17.000
[Audio description] The snowman pats him with a thin stick arm.

00:01:17.000 --> 00:01:19.600
[Audio description] Then he goes to sneeze.

00:01:19.600 --> 00:01:22.400
[Audio description] He grabs his nose with both hands.

00:01:22.400 --> 00:01:26.000
[Audio description] His head shoots off.

00:01:26.000 --> 00:01:30.000
[On-screen text] Frozen. Coming this winter in 3D.
